snippet.title: Jurassic World Aftermath  |  Launch Trailer  |  Oculus Quest Platform
snippet.description:
You've crash landed onto Isla Nublar and Velociraptors stalk your every move. Outsmart and outrun prehistoric predators in Jurassic World Aftermath, a thrilling new adventure game. Available now on Oculus Quest. 

https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/2708465082504733/

Learn more at oculus.com/jurassicworldaftermath
